<br>
I am back to playing my monk. She is lvl 35 now. I got some nice loot from my main (Magi) and I have now to choose a combo from my different weapons.<br>
<br>
I have right now :<br>
Ykeshan War Club<br>
Cane of the Tranquil *2<br>
Goranga Spiked Club<br>
<br>
